      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone who prioritizes function over form. The exterior shows some age with noticeable scratches on the passenger side and a small dent in the rear bumper, while the interior has some staining on the upholstery and minor wear on the steering wheel. Mechanically, it runs well and has been regularly serviced, though the air conditioning takes a moment to cool down and there is a slight squeak from the brakes that doesn't affect stopping power. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that will get you where you need to go without any hidden surprises.",
