    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this superlative automotive specimen, currently held in showroom condition. This vehicle exhibits an uncompromising level of preservation, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in its original, factory-fresh state. Meticulously maintained and mechanically absolute, this asset represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle of peerless integrity. Every detail confirms its status as a premier example of the marque.",
