    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a true time-capsule vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been protected by a professional ceramic coating, the exterior is absolutely flawless with no chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather seats are supple with zero bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage or imperfections. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented service history with every maintenance interval performed strictly at the dealership. It has been exclusively garage-kept and never driven in inclement weather. From the crisp response of the engine to the factory-fresh scent of the interior, this vehicle represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year and is ready for its next caretaker.",
      "price": 48500.0,
