    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014this car is a total gem! It\u2019s in truly pristine, showroom-quality condition and has been pampered since day one. Not a single scratch or dent to be found, and it drives as smooth as the day it was bought. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Come swing by and see it for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
