    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This example features the legendary S65 4.0L V8, delivering linear power with a stratospheric 8,400 RPM redline through eight individual throttle bodies. The chassis is impeccably preserved, retaining its factory-spec torsional rigidity and equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for precise lateral dynamics. Mechanically flawless, the M-Variable limited-slip differential and DCT gearbox provide lightning-fast actuation and crisp downshifts. Meticulously maintained with documented rod bearing service and a pristine subframe, this is a turn-key, showroom-quality specimen for the discerning purist.",
